    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Overview </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape a series of winding caves full of strange creatures and treacherous platforming challenges. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precise, responsive controls </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4-directional shooting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Linear side-scrolling level design</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000490/extras/9d8813ca054160842e40968a0190a5fc.poster.avif?t=1763240349\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000490/extras/9d8813ca054160842e40968a0190a5fc.webm?t=1763240349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000490/extras/9d8813ca054160842e40968a0190a5fc.mp4?t=1763240349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New enemies, hazards, and boss fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 levels across 3 worlds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built-in level editor</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Built-In Level Editor </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own levels using the built-in level editor. Import and export levels to share, play, and edit community-created content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000490/extras/72eb97648887c559ab7c4af0690e6826.poster.avif?t=1763240349\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste